defined_text = {
    name = GV_ID_Tag
    random = no
    text = {
        trigger = {
            NOT = { is_variable_equal = { which = aaa value = 0 } }
        }
        localisation_key = GV_ID_Tag
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GV_0
    }

defined_text = {
    name = GVL_SF_Wealth
    random = no
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVL_0
        trigger = {
            OR = {
                check_variable = { which = aai value = 1000 }
                NOT = { check_variable = { which = aai value = -1000 } }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVL_1
        trigger = {
            OR = {
                check_variable = { which = aai value = 100 }
                NOT = { check_variable = { which = aai value = -100 } }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {

        trigger = {

                check_variable = { which = aai value = 10 }
                NOT = { check_variable = { which = aai value = -10 } }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVL_3
    }
}
defined_text = {
    name = GVR_SF_Wealth
    random = no
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVR_33
        trigger = {
            variable_arithmetic_trigger = {
                export_to_variable = { which = temp value = 0 }
                change_variable = { which = temp which = aai }
                divide_variable = { which = temp value = 1000 }
                multiply_variable = { which = temp value = 1000 }
                subtract_variable = { which = temp which = aai }
                is_variable_equal = { which = temp value = 0 }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVR_32
        trigger = {
            variable_arithmetic_trigger = {
                export_to_variable = { which = temp value = 0 }
                change_variable = { which = temp which = aai }
                divide_variable = { which = temp value = 100 }
                multiply_variable = { which = temp value = 100 }
                subtract_variable = { which = temp which = aai }
                is_variable_equal = { which = temp value = 0 }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVR_31
        trigger = {
            variable_arithmetic_trigger = {
                export_to_variable = { which = temp value = 0 }
                change_variable = { which = temp which = aai }
                divide_variable = { which = temp value = 10 }
                multiply_variable = { which = temp value = 10 }
                subtract_variable = { which = temp which = aai }
                is_variable_equal = { which = temp value = 0 }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVR_0

    name = GVL_NM_SpendTax

                check_variable = { which = arz value = 1000 }
                NOT = { check_variable = { which = arz value = -1000 } }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {

            }

    random = no
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVL_0
        trigger = {
            OR = {

                NOT = { check_variable = { which = lvu value = -100000 } }
            }
        }
    }

        trigger = {

                NOT = { check_variable = { which = lvu value = -10000 } }
            }

        trigger = {

                check_variable = { which = lvu value = 1000 }
                NOT = { check_variable = { which = lvu value = -1000 } }
            }
        }
    }

        localisation_key = GVL_3
        trigger = {
            OR = {
                check_variable = { which = lvu value = 100 }
                NOT = { check_variable = { which = lvu value = -100 } }
            }

                change_variable = { which = temp which = lvu }
                divide_variable = { which = temp value = 1000 }
                multiply_variable = { which = temp value = 1000 }
                subtract_variable = { which = temp which = lvu }
                is_variable_equal = { which = temp value = 0 }
            }
        }
    }
    text = {
        localisation_key = GVR_0
    }
}
